===============================================================================
 sample 1 (Created in 2008)
===============================================================================

Functions file that contains all type of functions like database operations, url generator, form fields generator, ...

===============================================================================
 designhq (Created in August 2011)
===============================================================================

Wordpress theme based on HTML template "Design HQ" by Solucija (http://www.solucija.com/).
Works with wordpress 3.1.3 and later. 

===============================================================================
 sample 2 (Created in October 2012)
===============================================================================

PHP class that works with twitter getting tweets from a user. 
The samples folder contain examples that display latest tweets, hashtags used, tweets that only have urls, ...
In samples/conf.php you can setup twitter user, num of tweets to display and if you want to include retweets

